{"tid":62620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跨年夜悲劇】男子施放椰型煙火　遭炸爆頭慘死","createTime":"2017-01-01T05:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T09:25:44.000Z","uid":15410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"376a6385642a532cc89a09720b5e5d35e3aa586b","tid":62620,"uid":15410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170101/1025552/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flocal%2F20170101%2F1025552%2F&d=YbtR21lBoBPA9Rj5GNPUrksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f2f14b8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/local/20170101/1025552/</a><br />\n（新增：死者用打火機點高空煙火，不慎遭炸頭慘死）<br />\n新北市淡水屯山里溪口地區，今天凌晨0時一名蔡姓男子（32歲），疑似在倒數跨年時施放高空煙火，卻不慎發生爆炸，蔡男臉部遭炸倒地，頭顱破裂、流出大量鮮血，警消獲報後趕抵，發現蔡男面目全非、腦漿溢出，已經沒有生命跡象，警方立即封鎖現場調查。蔡男親友見到如此慘狀，情緒相當激動。<br />\n警方調查，死者蔡友章（32歲）自營小型鐵工廠，育有三女與家人同住；事發時，蔡男的張姓嬸嬸聽聞巨響外出查看，發現蔡男倒臥路旁，頭部疑遭煙火炸裂開當場死亡，趕緊通知家人與救護車，但蔡已明顯死亡，警方到場採證，發現蔡男腳邊有一長60公分、直徑11公分的圓筒長管，管內還殘有火藥味，蔡男身邊還留有打火機，初步推斷蔡男因放煙火不慎遭炸死。<br />\n警方說，蔡男應該是獨自一人在住處附近的產業道路，施放「禮花彈」型的煙火，才會利用高約60公分的纖維管，將直徑約10公分的椰型煙火彈放入，但是一般「禮花彈」通識透過電子引線點燃施放，而蔡男卻是用打火機直接點火，加上不熟「禮花彈」的爆裂原理，誤以為「禮花彈」沒點燃，探頭查看後遭煙火直接炸中頭部，當場頭顱破裂慘死，檢警除了將進行遺體相驗，更要追查煙火來源釐清案情。（突發中心／新北報導）"},{"pid":"0852c23b515fb95018095200a85a2f26c999fcfa","tid":62620,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"又係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6013d689807bcbe84645f3f31e99993b94ffbc8","tid":62620,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"細個記得有一單一樣 喺中國的"},{"pid":"c5437280c57a61bbdff2df931e90b697b8e88eeb","tid":62620,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"666666666"},{"pid":"47c8846615fed244b02ba140760d849a0afe11f0","tid":62620,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"死台狗弱撚智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d074dff35f3af1f11b0712483922f24494a5ec2","tid":62620,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"台灣人好似特別蠢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada3805a66b4202abd573d7f1c682471d38c73c0","tid":62620,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"新北市加一分"},{"pid":"c8579adf2f12016e942c8b3d724414da45e37371","tid":62620,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"諗起都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8617e7d9bcd7e05e53740680cd27105e16acd8a","tid":62620,"uid":15282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:56:41.000Z","msg":"冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e72fc0be56502c14c4aa8e2de043a5088bd1663","tid":62620,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戇鳩台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}